---

<Layout 
  title="How to Choose the Perfect Hair Extension Color (2024 Guide)"
  description="Expert guide on selecting the right hair extension color. Learn about color matching tools, common mistakes to avoid, and professional tips for a natural look."
  image="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1605980776566-0486c3ac7617?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80"
>
  <main class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 pt-24">
