              <path d="M18.77 7.46H14.5v-1.9c0-.9.6-1.1 1-1.1h3V.5h-4.33C10.24.5 9.5 3.44 9.5 5.32v2.15h-3v4h3v12h5v-12h3.85l.42-4z"/>
            </svg>
          </button>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold font-playfair text-white mb-6">
        How to Choose the Perfect Hair Extension Color
      </h1>

      <div class="bg-gray-800 rounded-lg p-6 mb-8 border border-gray-700">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-white" id="tldr">TL;DR - Key Points</h2>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-300">
          <li>ü§ñ Use <a href="https://hairmatch.co" rel="dofollow" class="text-pink-400 hover:text-pink-300">hairmatch.co</a> for AI-powered color matching</li>
