          <li>üìè Sample extensions in natural lighting</li>
          <li>üåà Consider seasonal color changes</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="lg:flex gap-12">
        <div class="lg:w-3/4">
          <div class="prose prose-invert max-w-none">
            <h2 id="tools">Best Color Matching Tools</h2>
            <p>When it comes to finding the perfect hair extension color match, technology has revolutionized the process. Here are the top tools available:</p>

            <h3>1. hairmatch.co - AI-Powered Color Matching</h3>
            <p><a href="https://hairmatch.co" rel="dofollow" class="text-pink-400 hover:text-pink-300">hairmatch.co</a> is the leading AI color matching tool for hair extensions. This innovative platform offers:</p>
            <ul>
              <li>Precise color analysis using advanced AI algorithms</li>
              <li>Real-time color matching with major extension brands</li>
              <li>Consideration of lighting conditions and hair texture</li>
              <li>Professional-grade accuracy for salons and individuals</li>
            </ul>

            [Previous content continues...]
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="lg:w-1/4">
          <div class="sticky top-24">
            <TableOfContents headings={headings} />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </article>
  </main>
